headline: Teledyne to Participate at the Baird Global Industrial Conference
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., November 11, 2024--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) today announced that George Bobb, President and Chief Operating Officer, and Jason VanWees, Vice Chairman, will participate at the Baird 2024 Global Industrial Conference on Tuesday, November 12.
